headline: Home Depot earnings, Fed, homebuilder confidence: What to Watch
summary: Market Domination Overtime host Josh Lipton previews several of the biggest stories to come tomorrow, Tuesday, November 18, including quarterly earnings results from companies like Home Depot (HD), Baidu (BIDU, 9888.HK), and Klarna (KLAR); the latest Homebuilder Confidence Index reading; and commentary from Federal Reserve governor Michael Barr. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Domination Overtime.
